---
title: Sri Lankan Style Sweet Potato Curry with Green Beans, Basmati Rice and Cashews
description: This Sri Lankan Style Sweet Potato Curry is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sri-lankan-style-sweet-potato-curry-524e7bff-f965b1d3.jpg
